{"tid":1085392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【裸漢出沒注意】光豬男將軍澳悠然散步 商場偷衫兼襲警","createTime":"2019-03-31T06:27:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-31T08:12:44.000Z","uid":39464,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f4bfe14cd71e797fe73921de50283fdeb6cb62d4","tid":1085392,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T06:27:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190331/_2019033113251696715.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190331%2F_2019033113251696715.jpg&h=681b1d42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n裸漢出沒注意！一名光豬男毋懼溫度驟降，早上在將軍澳寶琳一帶悠然散步。警員事後到場截獲有關的41歲男子，以涉嫌猥褻露體、盜竊及襲警將他拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方中午12時30分接報指，有人在現場懷疑猥褻露體。警員接報到場，男子以手襲擊一名警員，面及腳受傷的警員，及其他警務人員其後制服該名男子。警方經初步調查，男子懷疑曾在一店鋪盜取3件合約值350元的衣服。<br />\n<br />\n男子涉嫌猥褻露體、盜竊及襲警被捕，案件交由將軍澳警區刑事調查隊第四隊跟進。而受傷警員，清醒被送往將軍澳醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n網友拍到該名光豬男在港鐵寶琳外遊走，並將片段放上fb專頁「將軍澳西貢友 Friends of TKO &amp; Sai Kung」。另有網友在連接寶琳站的新都城二期商場見到光豬男，並指他「沖入去搶女士內衣」。<br />\n<br />\n有回應的網友更報料，指今早坐98D巴士時，「在茵怡花園都見到佢突然走上98D行了一個圈坐低咗，啲人立即走落車之後佢突然又落車，啲人立即衝上巴士，俾佢嚇死」。<br />\n<br />\n見到有人露鳥，好心的網民替他擔心，指「今天天氣凍喎，小心保暖」，並建議報警。不過，最多網友都提到「同框」出現的小新，指「小新都唔敢裸跑」、「小新睇到嘩一聲」。面對此情此景，有網友不禁大嘆「香港人太大壓力」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1469439/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1469439%2F&d=Sk6y7wLkZ8LsH37jlkaP9%2FRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=615b05f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1469439%2F&h=2eb251fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1469439/</a>"},{"pid":"40db920c6f4f802c6e18cbd9c28505a89ebb41e8","tid":1085392,"uid":8572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T06:32:50.000Z","msg":"邊位ching 找數"},{"pid":"a6e13ee0f3ba65030560c8384f19c6281b351959","tid":1085392,"uid":180184,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T06:33:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V7jeR0Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV7jeR0Q.jpg&h=19c70468&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c6131245c871db16af9122e060e9a8e41af0e6cd","tid":1085392,"uid":33848,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T06:36:30.000Z","msg":"「在茵怡花園都見到佢突然走上98D行了一個圈坐低咗，啲人立即走落車之後佢突然又落車，啲人立即衝上巴士，俾佢嚇死」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e32801f1f158bb89f3475808ee7590e816428e30","tid":1085392,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T06:36:31.000Z","msg":"近年好似多咗case? 香港人壓力大？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb9f9416d8758bc535da1963b73032bb64391bd8","tid":1085392,"uid":60651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T06:42:08.000Z","msg":"奇行種"},{"pid":"3f41af45df702485f551619eb5914b53bd84ba28","tid":1085392,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T06:43:49.000Z","msg":"告得入未"},{"pid":"4ed5d83d8c15de89bfdc1c9ab2fb0c4eaadbfdc5","tid":1085392,"uid":213319,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T06:43:55.000Z","msg":"麻煩樣貌好身材好先好當街祼露<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"901b42a27d09cc8372c594c9257a4788177a64be","tid":1085392,"uid":33907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6131245c871db16af9122e060e9a8e41af0e6cd","tid":1085392,"uid":33848,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T06:36:30.000Z","msg":"「在茵怡花園都見到佢突然走上98D行了一個圈坐低咗，啲人立即走落車之後佢突然又落車，啲人立即衝上巴士，俾佢嚇死」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTi